{"tid":387714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳曉東付費生日會快閃 僅送「簽名專CD」補償，歌迷憤怒","createTime":"2017-09-05T00:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T06:40:49.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b08f1e8decab3f6e650292e448ed801a8d804f","tid":387714,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:36:25.000Z","msg":"陳曉東以《心有獨鍾》、《心理遊戲》等歌紅遍兩岸三地，演藝事業橫跨影視歌領域的他，有大批死忠粉絲支持，不過在香港舉辦42歲生日粉絲見面會時，過程以身體不適突然離場，讓大批粉絲感到不滿。<br />\n<br />\n陳曉東在舉辦42歲生日會，來自全球各地的粉絲共襄盛舉，原先氣氛相當和樂卻突然變調，原來是罹患急性青光眼的陳曉東，因為眼睛感到不適中途就離場，這讓所有粉絲相當錯愕，畢竟繳了費用入場，偶像卻沒履行合照和簽名的承諾，對此經紀人出面解釋，五月住院觀察四天被診斷出葡萄膜炎，甚至有失明的危險，目前對閃光燈很敏感的他，是真的很不舒服才中途離開，並承諾會把沒簽完的CD補簽完，對此說詞粉絲不僅不買帳，還認為相當敷衍不被重視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳曉東生日會。(影片/陳曉東臉書)<br />\n對此許多粉絲留言灌爆陳曉東臉書，「支持20年根本白支持」、「見面會遲到又提早離場，很難讓人信服」、「補送簽名CD就想了事」?看來短時間內難平息粉絲怒火。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170905001507-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170905001507-260404&d=T6xoQvd6NSR2GGzZF4vtHf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2c89b81e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170905001507-260404</a><br />\n東火[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/05/083548_8ef7c37b4b391072a6384cc8e289bbb3.jpg[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F05%2F083548_8ef7c37b4b391072a6384cc8e289bbb3.jpg%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=T6xoQvd6NSR2GGzZF4vtHf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=928f407d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/05/083548_8ef7c37b4b391072a6384cc8e289bbb3.jpg[/img］</a><br />\n東東以為自己是華仔嗎"},{"pid":"d5953f7d05297aa2180d16a73276d1f5170b5c6c","tid":387714,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:42:03.000Z","msg":"賠錢咪得，唔識做"},{"pid":"253ed9198f94e62734c623ca30d041587faa783e","tid":387714,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:56:36.000Z","msg":"褻瀆神靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65c1b07a49df7d02f1c360d123c516aae385142","tid":387714,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"佢就算死左都要擺條屍出黎比人影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b61cd0c9b21385a59981fd672d16aca76891377","tid":387714,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T02:26:09.000Z","msg":"佢個樣愈來愈膠同拿形"},{"pid":"b2a5ad9720cfffd70300af64b763553a7b497fd2","tid":387714,"uid":40662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T02:44:08.000Z","msg":"做乜唔搵余迪偉頂住先？"},{"pid":"06d0b0430ab8b071b7303e87231b174754e7273b","tid":387714,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"整容整到走晒樣 勁膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d5179f07791703cb687e970c9dd124a9d72687","tid":387714,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾唔好叫自己做FANS啦 講到尾都係為張相即係合照黨 扮撚曬清高認做FANS"},{"pid":"37d805339154011a4e0692782d58400d28062e98","tid":387714,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜唔搵余迪偉頂住先？</blockquote><br />\n咁要加入埋迪偉俱樂部"},{"pid":"1d1a82bd9b59e2ef7d94c705732a86c01a15d7ac","tid":387714,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:39:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40492b857bd110195baf32666be6b0bf46b2b2a3","tid":387714,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做乜唔搵余迪偉頂住先？</blockquote><br />\n咁要加入埋迪偉俱樂部</blockquote><br />\n分唔到佢兩個"}]}